/**
 * OpenAI-compatible /v1/chat/completions server with full agentic loop.
 *
 * Bridges OpenAI API format → gnosis fat-station (native inference) +
 * mcp.forkjoin.ai (tool execution) via runAgenticChatCompletion.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   FAT_STATION_URL=http://localhost:8000 PORT=8080 tsx src/bin/openai-server.ts
 *
 * Env vars:
 *   FAT_STATION_URL   fat-station base URL (default: http://localhost:8000)
 *   PORT              listen port (default: 8080)
 *   MODEL_NAME        reported model name (default: gnosis-local)
 *   MCP_URL           MCP superserver URL (default: https://mcp.forkjoin.ai/mcp)
 *   MCP_AUTH_TOKEN    optional Bearer token for MCP
 *   THOTH_OATH_LEDGER_PATH optional JSON file for Thoth oath persistence
 *   STOP_TOKENS       comma-separated extra stop token IDs
 *   AGENTIC           set to "1" to default direct requests into tool mode
 *   TERMINAL_PROSODY  DEFAULT OFF (opt-in) until the prosody-speed work lands —
 *                     terminal-prosody biasing is ~15-19s/step on CPU. Set
 *                     "bias" to force it on globally, "observe" for telemetry-only.
 *                     Per request, voice/TTS callers opt in with `enable_prosody:true`
 *                     (or `terminal_prosody:"bias"|"observe"`); `suppress_prosody:true`
 *                     always wins as a belt-and-suspenders override.
 *   MOONSHINE_TTS_AUDIO_MODE auto|host|pulse|alsa|file (default: auto; compose uses host on macOS)
 *   AUX_KNOT_PATH     path to .knot file for in-process aux inference (intent-eval, tool-review, etc.)
 *   TOKENIZER_GGUF_PATH path to a GGUF carrying tokenizer metadata for Qwen models
 *   TOKENIZER_JSON_PATH path to a Hugging Face tokenizer.json for BPE/Metaspace models
 *   TOKENIZER_JSON_URL  URL to a Hugging Face tokenizer.json for BPE/Metaspace models
 *   TOKENIZER_FAMILY    explicit tokenizer family: llama | qwen2 | hf-bpe-metaspace
 *   MOONSHINE_ADMISSION_QSPEC_PATH optional serving qspec JSON path
 *   MOONSHINE_PREFILL_WINDOWS set "0" to disable explicit speculative prefill windows
 *   MOONSHINE_MAX_PROMPT_TOKENS prompt-token cap for local fat-station requests (default: prefill cap)
 *   MOONSHINE_DISABLE_NATIVE_GENERATE set "1" to force host-orchestrated decode
 */

